**B3 (Missing adjudication table):** Fixed. `docs/evidence/agentic-consensus-2026-07-09-phase-a-exit/adjudication.md` committed with round 1 (A1–A5) and round 2 (B1–B3) findings, categories, resolutions, and final disposition.

### 3. Category-(b) new definition nodes: **none to register**

Cursor's residual category-(b) note on detector enforcement semantics before fail-on-regression is already governed by `docs/heresy-detectors.md:7-9` deferring enforcement. No new definition node required.

